### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@authToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2YTFlODA2NjU5NzliZWVlNDFjZjVmNGIiLCJyb2xlSWQiOjIsImlhdCI6MTc4MDQ5NzgwNiwiZXhwIjoyNjQ0NDk3ODA2fQ.XSvrEpbwY_Jt6VjNaYIHmfnsHVQtPTXjSEsVy6H6XzE
@eventId = 6a2180d152e63cd63815fcfa

### 1. View Event Details (Triggers a view tracking log)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/details/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 2. Fetch Single Event Analytics (No filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 3. Fetch Single Event Analytics (Filter: last 7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/{{eventId}}?filter=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 4. Fetch Single Event Analytics (Filter: last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/{{eventId}}?filter=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 5. Fetch Single Event Analytics (Filter: this month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/{{eventId}}?filter=thisMonth
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 6. Fetch Single Event Analytics (Filter: custom date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/{{eventId}}?startDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&endDate=2026-06-10T23:59:59.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 7. Fetch Organizer's Events Analytics Summary (No filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 8. Fetch Organizer's Events Analytics Summary (Filter: last 7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/summary?filter=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 9. Fetch Organizer's Events Analytics Summary (Filter: custom date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/analytics/summary?startDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&endDate=2026-06-10T23:59:59.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
